  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dba \u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A budget secret out of Vajira",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party Chairman Mr. Vajira Abeywardena said that the president will present a budget that will give priority to the upliftment of the poor and develop the people with tax amendments.",
        "Mr. Abeywardhana said that this budget is presented as a revision budget, not to build roads and buildings, but to create a system for the people who do not have food and clothing to buy a mouthful of rice and clothes.",
        "Mr. Vajira Abiveardhana said that a generation of malnourished children is being born and as a solution to those problems, those who develop the people will present a tax with the presidential tax amendments and hope to quench the hunger of the suffering children. The UNP chairman also mentioned that action will be taken to correct the mistakes made by the previous government.",
        "Mr. Vajira Abeywardhana said that anyone can have dreams of being prime minister and president, but they should also have a plan to live the lives of two million twenty million people.",
        "Mr. Vajira Abiveardhana said this at a meeting held to inform the people of Galle about the 76th anniversary of the UNP."
      ],
